Team 1086 Blue Cheese is proud to release our 2025 CAD and Code for our Competition robot, Stringray!

Onshape

Github

image880×808 89.7 KB

Stringray can:

  • Drive

  • Intake coral from the Coral Station

  • Score on all 4 levels

  • Remove algae from the reef

  • Score algae in the net and in the processor

  • Climb on deep cages

Feel free to ask any questions you have!
